v> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="se_component se_paragraph default"> <div class="se_sectionArea"> <div class="se_editArea"> <div class="se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-justify" style="line-height: 250%;"> <div class="se_editView"> <div class="se_textView"> <p class="se_textarea"> <!-- SE3-TEXT { --> -&nbsp;종합자료실&nbsp;도서는&nbsp;중학생&nbsp;이상&nbsp;회원증으로&nbsp;상호대차&nbsp;신청이&nbsp;가능합니다. <br>-&nbsp;SMS&nbsp;수신동의&nbsp;해주셔야&nbsp;상호대차&nbsp;관련&nbsp;서비스&nbsp;문자를&nbsp;받으실&nbsp;수&nbsp;있습니다. <br>-&nbsp;도서관&nbsp;사정에&nbsp;의해&nbsp;상호대차&nbsp;순회도서관&nbsp;별&nbsp;도착시간이&nbsp;변동될&nbsp;수&nbsp;있습니다.&nbsp; <br>-&nbsp;상호대차&nbsp;신청도서는&nbsp;대출&nbsp;받을&nbsp;도서관에&nbsp;도착&nbsp;시,&nbsp;도착일&nbsp;포함&nbsp;3일이&nbsp;지나면&nbsp;자동반납&nbsp;처리됩니다.&nbsp; <br>-&nbsp;도서가&nbsp;대출받을&nbsp;도서관에&nbsp;도착&nbsp;시&nbsp;SMS를&nbsp;발송하므로&nbsp;이용에&nbsp;참고하세요! <br>-&nbsp;상호대차&nbsp;도서는&nbsp;신청하신&nbsp;본인&nbsp;외&nbsp;다른&nbsp;가족&nbsp;구성원&nbsp;명의로&nbsp;대출할&nbsp;수&nbsp;없습니다.&nbsp; <br>-&nbsp;책이음&nbsp;서비스&nbsp;탈퇴를&nbsp;원하시는&nbsp;경우&nbsp;도서관을&nbsp;방문하여&nbsp;회원&nbsp;탈퇴를&nbsp;요청하거나&nbsp;책이음서비스홈페이지(<a href="http://book.nl.go.kr/" target="_blank" class="se_link">http://book.nl.go.kr/</a>)에서&nbsp;회원탈퇴를&nbsp;하실&nbsp;수&nbsp;있습니다.&nbsp;단,&nbsp;대출중인&nbsp;도서가&nbsp;존재하거나,&nbsp;현재&nbsp;대출정지회원의&nbsp;상태에&nbsp;있는&nbsp;이용자는&nbsp;해당&nbsp;사유가&nbsp;종료될&nbsp;때&nbsp;까지&nbsp;탈퇴가&nbsp;불가능&nbsp;합니다.&nbsp;<b>*책이음서비스&nbsp;탈퇴로&nbsp;인해&nbsp;회원증&nbsp;재발행시&nbsp;수수료(1000원)이&nbsp;발생될&nbsp;수&nbsp;있습니다.</b> <!-- } SE3-TEXT --> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="se_component se_paragraph default"> <div class="se_sectionArea"> <div class="se_editArea"> <div class="se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-justify" style="line-height: 250%;"> <div class="se_editView"> <div class="se_textView"> <p class="se_textarea"> <!-- SE3-TEXT { --> <!-- } SE3-TEXT --> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="se_component se_horizontalLine default"> <div class="se_sectionArea"> <div class="se_editArea"> <div class